# Migrate explain

Static SQL safety preview for pending migrations. No DB required.

1. Run `gofasta migrate up --explain --strict --json`.
2. Report `max_risk`.
3. List every migration whose risk is `data-loss`, `lock-and-fill`,
   `lock-and-rewrite`, or `app-incompatibility`.
4. Ask the user before running `gofasta migrate up` if any
   high-severity warning fires.
